data.description: Come see this Beautiful South Lakeland Home!  This 4 bedroom 2 bathroom Pool home has been completely updated.  Family Room, Gourmet Kitchen with Updated Appliances, Huge Bfast Bar and Bfast Nook, Remodeled Bathrooms, Large Patio Overlooking Tranquil Pool and Oversized Backyard.  Garage Has Plenty of Storage and a Workshop for those who need the extra space.  Replaced Fence, Gutters and Windows 2013, A/C 2009, Roof 2011, Septic Pumped 2016, Saltwater Analyzer Replaced 2015, Termite Warranty 2017. Easy Access to the Polk Parkway and Shopping.  You will fall in love with this home!!!
